WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.166 --> 00:00:01.066
Recently, the

00:00:01.066 --> 00:00:03.266
registration threshold for TikTok US stores has been significantly lowered, and the

00:00:03.266 --> 00:00:05.766
overall daily GMV of these stores has repeatedly reached new highs. It is expected that by the end of

00:00:05.900 --> 00:00:07.066
this year and into next year,

00:00:07.066 --> 00:00:08.900
TikTok will open

00:00:08.900 --> 00:00:10.466
applications to more European and American countries, such as Spain.

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:11.900
However, many people are still unclear about the

00:00:11.900 --> 00:00:13.500
specific registration methods for US stores.

00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:14.366
So, in this video,

00:00:14.366 --> 00:00:15.933
I will explain in detail the

00:00:15.933 --> 00:00:17.699
various store types,

00:00:17.933 --> 00:00:18.866
current registration requirements,

00:00:18.866 --> 00:00:21.333
thresholds, and practical demonstrations of the specific store process. At

00:00:21.333 --> 00:00:23.466
the end of the video, I will also attach a

00:00:23.466 --> 00:00:24.399
super detailed version of the

00:00:24.399 --> 00:00:26.533
TikTok store operation guide and resource package compiled by our team.

00:00:26.533 --> 00:00:27.733
Don't miss it!

00:00:27.733 --> 00:00:28.333
Okay, here,

00:00:28.333 --> 00:00:30.366
I have summarized a

00:00:30.366 --> 00:00:32.500
mind map for TikTok store beginners.

00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:33.633
You can follow my steps

00:00:33.633 --> 00:00:35.233
to understand

00:00:35.233 --> 00:00:37.533
how to apply for and join a US store.

00:00:37.833 --> 00:00:39.299
First, we need to understand the

00:00:39.299 --> 00:00:39.766


00:00:39.766 --> 00:00:42.033
different store types in the US.

00:00:42.166 --> 00:00:42.899
Currently,

00:00:42.899 --> 00:00:45.633
US stores can be broadly divided into

00:00:45.633 --> 00:00:46.833
cross-border stores and local stores.

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:49.166
Cross-border stores are generally open to

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:50.166
mainland Chinese companies

00:00:50.166 --> 00:00:52.166
or Hong Kong companies.

00:00:52.233 --> 00:00:54.200
However, each cross-border store

00:00:54.200 --> 00:00:56.500
needs to pay a $500 deposit. The

00:00:56.833 --> 00:00:58.366
entry threshold for cross-border stores is

00:00:58.366 --> 00:00:59.600
shown here...

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:01.433
It requires

00:01:01.433 --> 00:01:03.033
you to first have a company license, and

00:01:03.033 --> 00:01:03.500
secondly,

00:01:03.500 --> 00:01:05.566
you need

00:01:05.599 --> 00:01:07.133
some experience operating other e-commerce platforms,

00:01:07.166 --> 00:01:08.433
such as Amazon's US site,

00:01:08.433 --> 00:01:10.366
eBay/Walmart's US site, or

00:01:10.366 --> 00:01:13.033
a DTC independent site in the US market.

00:01:13.033 --> 00:01:13.700


00:01:13.700 --> 00:01:14.266
Long-time

00:01:14.266 --> 00:01:16.099
followers of mine may already be operating several

00:01:16.099 --> 00:01:17.099
independent sites, so

00:01:17.099 --> 00:01:19.266
you can use your independent site to apply and join. But what

00:01:19.366 --> 00:01:20.299
if you don't have the

00:01:20.299 --> 00:01:22.000
qualifications for these e-commerce platforms?

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:22.500


00:01:22.500 --> 00:01:22.700
Actually, you

00:01:22.700 --> 00:01:24.700
can also solve this through a service provider. I

00:01:24.833 --> 00:01:26.200
also welcome serious and

00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:27.799
reliable service providers to contact me,

00:01:27.799 --> 00:01:29.200
and I can recommend some.

00:01:29.333 --> 00:01:30.500
Okay, besides cross-border stores,

00:01:30.500 --> 00:01:31.533
we also have another type of store, which

00:01:31.533 --> 00:01:33.000
is the US domestic store. The

00:01:33.099 --> 00:01:34.133
US domestic store

00:01:34.133 --> 00:01:36.066
can be divided into two types:

00:01:36.066 --> 00:01:37.400
one is the US-owned store,

00:01:37.533 --> 00:01:39.733
and the other is called the ACCU store.

00:01:39.733 --> 00:01:41.900
The ACCU store means a US domestic store owned by a Chinese-funded American company.

00:01:41.900 --> 00:01:43.333


00:01:43.599 --> 00:01:44.200
Generally speaking, a

00:01:44.200 --> 00:01:45.299
normal US domestic store is

00:01:45.299 --> 00:01:47.166
divided into individual stores and corporate stores.

00:01:47.166 --> 00:01:49.566
The individual store, as the name suggests, is for US individuals.

00:01:49.566 --> 00:01:50.500
US local individuals

00:01:50.500 --> 00:01:52.099
can apply and join with their passport, driver's

00:01:52.099 --> 00:01:54.299
license, SSN number,

00:01:54.333 --> 00:01:56.000
or ITIN number.

00:01:56.000 --> 00:01:58.099


00:01:58.400 --> 00:01:59.200
The corporate store...

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:00.966
Besides needing an SSN

00:02:00.966 --> 00:02:02.733
or ITIN,

00:02:02.733 --> 00:02:04.533
you also need a US company. You apply and register

00:02:04.533 --> 00:02:06.466
through this US company's qualifications. The main

00:02:06.466 --> 00:02:07.733


00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:09.300
difference between these two

00:02:09.300 --> 00:02:09.866
is the order limit

00:02:09.866 --> 00:02:11.366
in the initial "newbie zone."

00:02:11.366 --> 00:02:13.366


00:02:13.466 --> 00:02:15.333
Secondly, there's the ACCU store, which stands for

00:02:15.333 --> 00:02:16.599
Chinese-owned US enterprise

00:02:16.733 --> 00:02:18.400
store. This means

00:02:18.400 --> 00:02:21.500
you can register a US company as a Chinese citizen and

00:02:21.500 --> 00:02:23.166


00:02:23.166 --> 00:02:25.000
apply to open a US store. Specifically,

00:02:25.366 --> 00:02:26.333


00:02:26.333 --> 00:02:28.699
you need a US entity with

00:02:28.699 --> 00:02:31.533
at least 25% Chinese legal representative.

00:02:31.533 --> 00:02:32.633
You also need to have

00:02:32.633 --> 00:02:34.233
inventory in the US and

00:02:34.333 --> 00:02:34.966


00:02:34.966 --> 00:02:37.000


00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:39.033
proof of operation from a third-party e-commerce platform.

00:02:39.033 --> 00:02:39.833
This proof is similar to the

00:02:39.833 --> 00:02:40.866


00:02:40.866 --> 00:02:43.833
application materials for cross-border stores.

00:02:43.833 --> 00:02:44.733


00:02:44.966 --> 00:02:46.333
Some might ask about the

00:02:46.466 --> 00:02:47.533
operational differences between

00:02:47.533 --> 00:02:49.566
cross-border and domestic stores. There

00:02:49.633 --> 00:02:51.599
are two main differences.

00:02:51.599 --> 00:02:53.266
First, the organic traffic of the marketplace.

00:02:53.566 --> 00:02:56.133
Based on our own experience and

00:02:56.133 --> 00:02:57.566
feedback from others, the

00:02:57.566 --> 00:02:59.433
organic traffic of US domestic stores is generally

00:02:59.566 --> 00:03:00.466
greater than that of

00:03:00.466 --> 00:03:01.699
cross-border stores.

00:03:01.833 --> 00:03:04.166
Secondly, there's the official shipping subsidy,

00:03:04.166 --> 00:03:06.500
which is a higher percentage for local stores than for

00:03:06.500 --> 00:03:09.933
cross-border stores.

00:03:09.933 --> 00:03:11.533
Besides the

00:03:11.533 --> 00:03:14.066
application materials for different stores I just mentioned, a mandatory requirement for all

00:03:14.166 --> 00:03:15.966
US small stores is

00:03:15.966 --> 00:03:17.166


00:03:17.166 --> 00:03:18.266


00:03:18.266 --> 00:03:19.699
having

00:03:19.699 --> 00:03:21.333
a source of goods in the US.

00:03:21.333 --> 00:03:22.866
Whether you use someone else's warehouse, ship directly,

00:03:22.866 --> 00:03:24.433


00:03:24.433 --> 00:03:26.533
or use any other shipping method,

00:03:26.533 --> 00:03:27.133


00:03:27.133 --> 00:03:28.933
your logistics must originate

00:03:28.933 --> 00:03:30.566
from within the US.

00:03:30.666 --> 00:03:31.199
For example,

00:03:31.199 --> 00:03:31.666
some people

00:03:31.666 --> 00:03:33.466
previously used virtual warehouses

00:03:33.466 --> 00:03:34.199
for shipping, but this will

00:03:34.199 --> 00:03:34.800


00:03:34.800 --> 00:03:36.866
definitely be penalized by the platform.

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:38.833
Since I've already posted about the

00:03:38.833 --> 00:03:40.599
registration process for US local stores,

00:03:40.666 --> 00:03:42.400
today we'll use cross-border stores as an

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:43.599
example to explain the

00:03:43.599 --> 00:03:47.233
preparation materials and specific onboarding process for opening a TikTok store. For

00:03:47.233 --> 00:03:48.566
US cross-border stores,

00:03:48.566 --> 00:03:49.000
firstly,

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:51.266
we need a business license from a mainland China company

00:03:51.266 --> 00:03:52.866
or a Hong Kong company.

00:03:53.266 --> 00:03:54.166
Secondly,

00:03:54.166 --> 00:03:55.233
you need the

00:03:55.233 --> 00:03:56.199


00:03:56.233 --> 00:03:58.433
legal representative's ID corresponding to the company's business license. Thirdly, you

00:03:58.633 --> 00:04:00.266
need a

00:04:00.266 --> 00:04:01.333
unique mobile phone number

00:04:01.333 --> 00:04:02.133
or email address.

00:04:02.199 --> 00:04:03.566
This is because some people

00:04:03.566 --> 00:04:05.433
may have already applied for other...

00:04:05.433 --> 00:04:06.800


00:04:06.933 --> 00:04:09.133
If you've already applied for another TikTok shop, it's not appropriate to use the

00:04:09.133 --> 00:04:11.266
same phone number and email address

00:04:11.266 --> 00:04:12.000
to apply again. The

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:12.866


00:04:13.066 --> 00:04:14.800
fifth point, as mentioned earlier, is that

00:04:14.800 --> 00:04:16.800
you need proof of a third-party e-commerce platform

00:04:16.800 --> 00:04:18.766
or independent website store. There are

00:04:18.966 --> 00:04:20.800
two ways to solve this: one is to

00:04:20.800 --> 00:04:22.000
solve it yourself, and the

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:24.033
other is to find a service provider.

00:04:24.033 --> 00:04:25.699
Generally, that's the approach.

00:04:25.699 --> 00:04:27.100
I'd also like to briefly mention

00:04:27.100 --> 00:04:28.133
that many people might be hesitant at this point, but

00:04:28.133 --> 00:04:29.533


00:04:29.533 --> 00:04:31.300
don't overcomplicate it.

00:04:31.300 --> 00:04:32.866
Currently,

00:04:32.933 --> 00:04:34.933
because we're approaching Q4,

00:04:34.933 --> 00:04:37.166
platforms are relatively lenient with store onboarding reviews, at

00:04:37.300 --> 00:04:38.833


00:04:38.833 --> 00:04:40.699
least for cross-border stores. Don't let

00:04:40.833 --> 00:04:42.433
this requirement

00:04:42.433 --> 00:04:44.699
create a negative impression; it's

00:04:44.699 --> 00:04:45.833
unnecessary. The

00:04:45.833 --> 00:04:46.666
fifth point is that

00:04:46.666 --> 00:04:47.899
you need a

00:04:47.899 --> 00:04:50.666
warehouse address in the US for shipping and returns. Regarding

00:04:50.866 --> 00:04:52.033
this warehouse address,

00:04:52.033 --> 00:04:54.166
we need to pay attention.

00:04:54.166 --> 00:04:56.733


00:04:56.733 --> 00:04:58.366
When small shops in the US ship goods, they

00:04:58.366 --> 00:05:00.033
usually

00:05:00.033 --> 00:05:02.300
either ship the products themselves

00:05:02.300 --> 00:05:03.366
by sea

00:05:03.433 --> 00:05:04.533
to the US

00:05:04.533 --> 00:05:07.100
and then ship them from an overseas warehouse there.

00:05:07.100 --> 00:05:08.266


00:05:08.333 --> 00:05:09.433
Another method...

00:05:09.433 --> 00:05:10.766
We can directly find

00:05:10.766 --> 00:05:13.133
some sellers in the US who have stockpiled goods and

00:05:13.133 --> 00:05:14.966
have local inventory.

00:05:14.966 --> 00:05:16.866
We can then ship through their inventory.

00:05:17.166 --> 00:05:18.500
Here, we need to be careful to

00:05:18.500 --> 00:05:18.833


00:05:18.833 --> 00:05:21.033
avoid using warehouse addresses that have been abused.

00:05:21.033 --> 00:05:22.533


00:05:22.633 --> 00:05:23.266


00:05:23.266 --> 00:05:25.133
I've heard feedback from users that using

00:05:25.133 --> 00:05:25.666


00:05:25.666 --> 00:05:27.833


00:05:27.833 --> 00:05:29.533
such addresses could

00:05:29.633 --> 00:05:31.766
lead to your

00:05:31.766 --> 00:05:33.300
account being banned by TikTok.

00:05:33.300 --> 00:05:34.733
Okay, now that we understand the application materials for a

00:05:34.733 --> 00:05:36.100
TikTok US cross-border store,

00:05:36.100 --> 00:05:37.966


00:05:37.966 --> 00:05:38.933
we can

00:05:38.933 --> 00:05:41.800
officially begin the application process. The

00:05:41.866 --> 00:05:43.166
application process is

00:05:43.166 --> 00:05:44.300
actually quite simple, with only

00:05:44.300 --> 00:05:45.266
5 steps. The

00:05:45.266 --> 00:05:45.966
first step is to register an account

00:05:45.966 --> 00:05:47.300
on the official TikTok

00:05:47.300 --> 00:05:48.733
cross-border store website.

00:05:48.733 --> 00:05:50.633
Remember, it's the official cross-border store website,

00:05:50.633 --> 00:05:52.066
not the local store website; the

00:05:52.066 --> 00:05:53.833
URLs are different. The

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:55.600


00:05:55.600 --> 00:05:56.466


00:05:56.466 --> 00:05:59.066
second step is to

00:05:59.066 --> 00:06:00.366
select North America and the United States as the countries you wish to sell to, and

00:06:00.366 --> 00:06:01.600
then choose either

00:06:01.600 --> 00:06:03.399
Mainland China or Hong Kong as the entity. The

00:06:03.666 --> 00:06:04.433
third step is to

00:06:04.433 --> 00:06:05.966
submit some certification materials,

00:06:05.966 --> 00:06:07.000
such as your business license,

00:06:07.000 --> 00:06:07.833
your legal representative's ID card, and other third-party certifications.  The

00:06:07.833 --> 00:06:09.133


00:06:09.166 --> 00:06:10.233


00:06:10.266 --> 00:06:11.066
fourth step

00:06:11.066 --> 00:06:12.566
is to fill in some basic information about your store,

00:06:12.566 --> 00:06:13.933
such as your store name

00:06:14.100 --> 00:06:16.133
and main product category. The

00:06:16.433 --> 00:06:18.600
last step is to wait for approval. The

00:06:18.600 --> 00:06:20.366
entire onboarding process

00:06:20.366 --> 00:06:21.066
is very simple.

00:06:21.066 --> 00:06:22.666
Let's demonstrate it in practice.

00:06:22.666 --> 00:06:24.366
First, we go to the

00:06:24.366 --> 00:06:26.366
official website of TikTok US cross-border store.

00:06:26.366 --> 00:06:28.166
We enter

00:06:28.166 --> 00:06:30.466
our mobile phone number, email address,

00:06:30.466 --> 00:06:31.533
and password.

00:06:31.533 --> 00:06:33.233
Then we click "Sign up"

00:06:33.233 --> 00:06:35.033
to register an account.

00:06:35.066 --> 00:06:36.233
Then we can enter the

00:06:36.233 --> 00:06:37.899
specific onboarding application process.

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:38.833
Here,

00:06:38.833 --> 00:06:40.600
we first need to select

00:06:40.600 --> 00:06:41.366
a specific market.

00:06:41.366 --> 00:06:42.466
We can choose North America

00:06:42.633 --> 00:06:43.899
and then the United States. For the

00:06:44.066 --> 00:06:44.833
onboarding method,

00:06:44.833 --> 00:06:46.266
we fill in "

00:06:46.266 --> 00:06:47.399
normal onboarding". For the

00:06:47.399 --> 00:06:48.966
company's location,

00:06:48.966 --> 00:06:50.233
we fill in Mainland China.

00:06:50.233 --> 00:06:51.433
Then we click "Continue". The

00:06:51.966 --> 00:06:53.333
next step

00:06:53.333 --> 00:06:55.633
is to submit some qualification certifications. For

00:06:55.766 --> 00:06:56.866
qualification certification,

00:06:56.866 --> 00:06:58.366
we first need to upload

00:06:58.366 --> 00:07:00.166
our company's business license.

00:07:00.166 --> 00:07:01.966
Then we click "Add Document".

00:07:02.433 --> 00:07:04.000
After clicking "Add Document", the

00:07:04.066 --> 00:07:06.433
company name

00:07:06.433 --> 00:07:08.533
and business license number will be automatically displayed.

00:07:09.366 --> 00:07:10.100
Then

00:07:10.100 --> 00:07:11.433
we can fill in the

00:07:11.433 --> 00:07:12.933
specific company registration address.

00:07:12.933 --> 00:07:14.233
The company registration address

00:07:14.233 --> 00:07:15.500
must be consistent with the registration address on your business license.

00:07:15.500 --> 00:07:16.466


00:07:16.466 --> 00:07:17.266


00:07:17.533 --> 00:07:19.266
Then we fill in the registration date

00:07:19.266 --> 00:07:21.066
and the validity period of the business license.

00:07:21.066 --> 00:07:23.166
Everything must match your business license. There's also

00:07:23.166 --> 00:07:24.833
a small option here where you

00:07:24.833 --> 00:07:26.333
need to fill in

00:07:26.333 --> 00:07:29.100
whether your company has an ultimate beneficial owner.

00:07:29.100 --> 00:07:29.333
We

00:07:29.333 --> 00:07:30.166
'll select "yes" here.

00:07:30.166 --> 00:07:31.033
Next, we need to

00:07:31.033 --> 00:07:32.866
verify the legal representative's information. There

00:07:32.933 --> 00:07:34.533
are three ways to verify this:

00:07:34.533 --> 00:07:36.133
you can upload your mainland ID card,

00:07:36.133 --> 00:07:38.533
a Hong Kong resident ID card,

00:07:38.866 --> 00:07:40.333
or your passport.

00:07:40.566 --> 00:07:42.633
We'll upload your ID card here.

00:07:43.100 --> 00:07:44.666
After uploading your ID card,

00:07:44.666 --> 00:07:46.866
we need to fill in the English name of

00:07:47.166 --> 00:07:48.566
our legal representative (which

00:07:48.566 --> 00:07:49.899


00:07:49.899 --> 00:07:50.833
is actually the pinyin).

00:07:50.833 --> 00:07:51.933
Write the pinyin down, and confirm the

00:07:51.933 --> 00:07:54.133
validity period

00:07:54.133 --> 00:07:57.266
and document number are correct.

00:07:57.266 --> 00:07:59.033
Then we can move on to the next step. The

00:07:59.533 --> 00:08:00.133
next step

00:08:00.133 --> 00:08:02.733
requires providing

00:08:02.733 --> 00:08:05.100
proof of operation from a third-party e-commerce platform. There are

00:08:05.133 --> 00:08:06.633


00:08:06.633 --> 00:08:08.266
roughly three types of proof of operation:

00:08:08.266 --> 00:08:10.033
eBay/Walmart,

00:08:10.033 --> 00:08:11.833
Amazon, and

00:08:11.933 --> 00:08:13.300
independent websites.

00:08:13.300 --> 00:08:14.633
We'll choose and submit according to your

00:08:14.633 --> 00:08:16.699
own situation.

00:08:16.699 --> 00:08:18.733


00:08:19.100 --> 00:08:19.699
Later,

00:08:19.699 --> 00:08:21.899
I will also attach a specific example of a store operation certificate

00:08:21.899 --> 00:08:22.766


00:08:22.766 --> 00:08:23.966
to this video

00:08:23.966 --> 00:08:26.100
or put it in our information package, which

00:08:26.100 --> 00:08:27.366
you can get yourself. The

00:08:27.733 --> 00:08:28.466
third step

00:08:28.466 --> 00:08:28.666
is...  You'll

00:08:28.666 --> 00:08:31.066
need to provide some basic information about your store.

00:08:31.066 --> 00:08:32.833
First, you need to enter a

00:08:32.833 --> 00:08:35.166
unique English name for your store.

00:08:35.166 --> 00:08:37.700
You can use any name you like.

00:08:37.833 --> 00:08:40.366
Then, you need to choose a main category. It's important to

00:08:40.366 --> 00:08:42.399
note that

00:08:42.399 --> 00:08:43.766
when choosing a main category, it's

00:08:43.766 --> 00:08:46.633
best to choose the category you actually want to operate in.

